    <div id="school-day" class="content-section">
      <h1>School Day</h1>
      <p>First Term: Sept - Dec<br>Second Term: Jan - April</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Morning Assembly:</strong> 7:30am – 8:00am. Prayer, announcements, and flag raising.</li>
        <li><strong>Academic Sessions:</strong> 8:00am – 12:30pm. Core subjects including Math, English, Science, and Social Studies.</li>
        <li><strong>Break Time:</strong> 10:30am – 11:00am. Recess and healthy snacks.</li>
        <li><strong>Afternoon Classes:</strong> 12:30pm – 2:00pm. Arts, Physical Education, and elective subjects.</li>
        <li><strong>Extracurricular Activities:</strong> 2:00pm – 3:00pm. Sports, clubs, and creative programs.</li>
        <li><strong>Closing:</strong> 3:00pm – 3:30pm. Review of the day and dismissal.</li>
      </ul>
      <img src="/images/people/successful-schoolgirl_1098-13593.avif" alt="Prep School Day" style="max-width: 100%; margin-top: 1em; border-radius: 8px;" loading="lazy">
